Titolo: Holiday Island (video game)

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: Holiday Island is a business simulation video game developed by German games design company Sunflower. Much of the game play involves juggling funds to build hotels, accommodation, leisure activities and restaurants. The number and location of these is important, as is the interconnectivity between different facilities. There are also other people like the player constructing and starting businesses in the island. The player can hire a Mafia style hitman to ruin the other people's businesses.

Genere: Strategy

Valutazione: N/A
